{
  "stem": "23942.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was very learned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Dvar Torah-- he said to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When-- before he died, he said he remembered the Dvar Torah-- my grandfather said to the Bluzhiver Rav.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he came to see him when he became the rav.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my zayde, my grandfather, my mother's father was very Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He had a beard-- and he, he wore a beard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was very Hasidic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was a nice man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And people liked him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And somebody told me he was even considered somewhat, in her exact word in Yiddish, somewhat not poor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In other words, he, he had-- he was considered somewhat-- for that village, he was considered not poor but somewhat, you know, affluent, in a way.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Jossel Susswein.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's a very unusual name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because anybody who spelled it this-- that way-- S-U-S-S, with a little dot on the top, on the U-- this was the from the same family originated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the way I found out why this is spelled like this-- because the first grandfather Susswein that we know of made wine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he, he came from near Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he settled in, in the town of Lesko, which is very far south in Poland, near Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he settled there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he-- they-- and he-- that's why he was named Susswein, Susswein.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's the reason why the name was-- you know, when names were given, way back in the centuries.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's where the name originates.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Susswein-- and I love that name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I think it's pretty, sounds pretty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I love that grandfather.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my mother had so much respect for her parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was the-- very respectful and loved her parents very much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she was the oldest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, and I remember such fond memories.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
